🎮 CodSoft Python Internship – Task 4 Completed: Rock-Paper-Scissors Game 🐍

I'm delighted to share that I have successfully completed Task 4 of my Python Programming Internship at CodSoft by creating a Rock-Paper-Scissors Game using Python.

This project was both enjoyable and educational. It helped me strengthen my understanding of programming logic, user interaction, and random number generation while creating an engaging command-line game.

📌 Project Overview

The application allows users to play Rock-Paper-Scissors against the computer. The computer randomly selects its move, compares it with the user's choice, and displays whether the user wins, loses, or draws.

✨ Key Features

✅ Interactive user interface

✅ Random computer selection

✅ Automatic winner determination

✅ Score tracking for multiple rounds

✅ Play-again option

✅ Input validation

